'''GKEY''' - "Grabs" the current selection and allows you to move it around with the mouse. Hold down '''SHIFT''' while moving for finer control. Use '''LMB''', '''ENTER''', or '''SPACE''' to drop it in place. Use '''RMB''' or '''ESC''' to cancel the move.<br>
