{{dropimage|hbgc=papayawhip|hfs=1.2em|width=500px|align=center|Heading style extract|CSS Heading Styles from [http://en.wikipedia.org/skins-1.5/monobook/main.css main.css] <pre style="font-size:1em;font-family:Arial,Sans-serif;">
